    "description": "准备好进入 <strong>Skyline Savior</strong> 的高速、充满动作的世界吧！<br><br>控制萨姆的汽车，穿越一系列令人兴奋和具有挑战性的环境。利用你独特的技能组合，克服困难的障碍，成为天空中的终极英雄。<br><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><u>激动人心的游戏机制</u></h2></strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>街机风格的汽车运动</strong>: 享受流畅且响应迅速的驾驶体验，可以跳跃、加速并执行酷炫的特技。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3122710/extras/d168ee9e92133daf8c5087317ccaf288.poster.avif?t=1746032406\" width=320 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3122710/extras/d168ee9e92133daf8c5087317ccaf288.webm?t=1746032406\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3122710/extras/d168ee9e92133daf8c5087317ccaf288.mp4?t=1746032406\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br></li><li><strong>磁铁</strong>: 利用汽车上的磁铁与地图上的各种磁铁互动，通过吸引或排斥汽车来克服障碍。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3122710/extras/704e184774d3b2069f3e38f31a3db3fb.poster.avif?t=1746032406\" width=320 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3122710/extras/704e184774d3b2069f3e38f31a3db3fb.webm?t=1746032406\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3122710/extras/704e184774d3b2069f3e38f31a3db3fb.mp4?t=1746032406\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br></li><li><strong>慢动作</strong>: 放慢时间，以便穿越复杂的序列和完成精确的操作。你正在下落？放慢时间，等待加速技能的冷却时间结束。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3122710/extras/98491e145a625d119898ee6d781fbaa9.poster.avif?t=1746032406\" width=320 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3122710/extras/98491e145a625d119898ee6d781fbaa9.webm?t=1746032406\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3122710/extras/98491e145a625d119898ee6d781fbaa9.mp4?t=1746032406\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br></li><li><strong>加速与下压力</strong>: 使用加速能力获得一阵速度爆发，迅速覆盖距离。激活下压力技能，将汽车压向地面，像反向跳跃一样，使你能够精确着陆并执行新的战略动作。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3122710/extras/8f1c27fd3ed48aee86446896562d0dea.poster.avif?t=1746032406\" width=320 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3122710/extras/8f1c27fd3ed48aee86446896562d0dea.webm?t=1746032406\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3122710/extras/8f1c27fd3ed48aee86446896562d0dea.mp4?t=1746032406\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></li></ul><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><u>游戏模式</u></h2></strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>普通模式</strong>: 在具有战略性控制点的关卡中导航，允许你从关键点重新生成并继续。<br></li><li><strong>相当困难模式</strong>: 接受终极挑战，从头到尾没有控制点，将你的技能和耐力推向极限。<br></li><li><strong>不可能模式</strong>: 除了没有控制点之外，你还没有加速和增强技能！需要更多挑战？磁铁现在有时间限制。祝你好运！</li></ul>",
